item.title: Need help pls
item.dc:creator: @Exist2inspire Exist2inspire
item.description:
@Exist2inspire wrote:

for the quest stuff, open up your client.JAVA and search for:

public void loadquestinterface()

under it, you will see everything in your quest tab, so just get rid of what you don’t want. and add what you want.

and for the logout stuff, open up your client.JAVA and search for:

	public void update()

under that you will see what it says in the logout button…

Enjoy.

PS: Cryme tyme, if im a dumbfuck and i just helped him, what does that make you??
